message.entry: YData must be a vector or matrix of type real numeric.
Passing xgroupdata is not supported when ydata is a matrix.
Setting XData is not supported when YData is a matrix.
YData cannot be a matrix when ''SourceTable'' property is non-empty.
xgroupdata must be the same size as ydata.
XData must be the same size as YData.
''GroupByColor'' parameter is not supported when the sample data argument is a matrix.
''GroupByColor'' parameter is not supported with table input.
''GroupByColor'' value must be the same size as the sample data argument.
Changing the ''Orientation'' property is not supported when the box chart has categorical values in multiple y-axes.
Changing the ''Orientation'' property is not supported when the box chart has categorical values and the axes contains charts of different types.
